{"tha-ap86:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap86:0.2":"Timiravagga ","tha-ap86:0.3":"Adhopupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap86:1.1":"“Abhibhu nama so bhikkhu, ","tha-ap86:1.2":"sikhino aggasavako; ","tha-ap86:1.3":"Mahanubhavo tevijjo, ","tha-ap86:1.4":"himavantam upagami. ","tha-ap86:2.1":"Ahampi himavantamhi, ","tha-ap86:2.2":"ramaniyassame isi; ","tha-ap86:2.3":"Vasami appamannasu, ","tha-ap86:2.4":"iddhisu ca tada vasi. ","tha-ap86:3.1":"Pakkhijato viyakase, ","tha-ap86:3.2":"pabbatam adhivatthayim; ","tha-ap86:3.3":"Adhopuppham gahetvana, ","tha-ap86:3.4":"agacchim pabbatam aham. ","tha-ap86:4.1":"Satta pupphani ganhitva, ","tha-ap86:4.2":"matthake okirim aham; ","tha-ap86:4.3":"Alokite ca virena, ","tha-ap86:4.4":"pakkamim pacinamukho. ","tha-ap86:5.1":"Avasam abhisambhosim, ","tha-ap86:5.2":"patvana assamam aham; ","tha-ap86:5.3":"Kharibharam gahetvana, ","tha-ap86:5.4":"payasim pabbatantaram. ","tha-ap86:6.1":"Ajagaro mam pilesi, ","tha-ap86:6.2":"ghorarupo mahabbalo; ","tha-ap86:6.3":"Pubbakammam saritvana, ","tha-ap86:6.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap86:7.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap86:7.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap86:7.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap86:7.4":"pupphapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap86:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap86:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap86:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap86:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma adhopupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap86:10.1":"Adhopupphiyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}